<%- headings = %w{FirstName Surname Coming Age   
	              Gender Days Address Suburb Postcode Phone Mobile 
	              Email Medicare MedicalInfo Medications YearsAttended
				  Spectator Onsite Helper GC Driver NumberPlate
				  DietaryRqmts EmergContact EmergRel EmergPhone 
				  WWCC } -%>
<%= headings.join(',') %>
<%= CSV.generate do |csv|
  @participants.each do |participant|
  	line = [ participant.first_name,
			 participant.surname,
  		     participant.coming,
  		     participant.age,
  		     participant.gender,
  		     participant.days,
  		     participant.address,
  		     participant.suburb,
  		     participant.postcode,
  		     participant.phone_number,
  		     participant.mobile_phone_number,
  		     participant.email,
  		     participant.medicare_number,
			 participant.medical_info,
			 participant.medications,
			 participant.years_attended,
			 participant.spectator,
			 participant.onsite,
			 participant.helper,
			 participant.group_coord,
			 participant.driver,
			 participant.number_plate,
			 participant.dietary_requirements,
			 participant.emergency_contact,
			 participant.emergency_relationship,
			 participant.emergency_phone_number,
			 participant.wwcc_number
		   ]
    csv << line
  end
end.html_safe %>
